Uses of Package
edu.rit.m2mi

Packages that use edu.rit.m2mi
edu.rit.m2mi Package edu.rit.m2mi is the API for Many-to-Many Invocation (M2MI). 
edu.rit.slides Package edu.rit.slides contains Slides, a service and collaborative application based on Many-to-Many Invocation (M2MI). 
 

Classes in edu.rit.m2mi used by edu.rit.m2mi
Eoid
          Class Eoid encapsulates an exported object identifier (EOID).
ExportMap
          Class ExportMap is the abstract base class for a mapping that stores exported objects.
Handle
          Class Handle is the abstract base class for all M2MI handle objects.
Invocation
          Class Invocation is the abstract base class for all invocation objects in M2MI.
InvocationFactory
          Class InvocationFactory is the abstract base class for a factory object that creates Invocation objects.
InvocationQueue
          Class InvocationQueue provides a queue of Invocation objects waiting to be processed.
M2MIClassLoader
          Class M2MIClassLoader provides a class loader for the M2MI Layer's synthesized handle classes and method invoker classes.
M2MIInitializationException
          Class M2MIInitializationException indicates that initialization of the M2MI Layer failed.
M2MIMessagePrefix
          Class M2MIMessagePrefix provides a bag of M2MI message prefixes registered with the M2MP Layer.
M2MIRuntimeException
          Class M2MIRuntimeException is the common base class for all unchecked RuntimeExceptions in M2MI.
MethodDescriptor
          Class MethodDescriptor provides an object that describes a target method for an M2MI call.
MethodInvoker
          Class MethodInvoker is the abstract base class for all synthesized method invoker classes in M2MI.
Multihandle
          Class Multihandle is the base class for all M2MI multihandle objects.
Omnihandle
          Class Omnihandle is the base class for all M2MI omnihandle objects.
Synthesizer
          Class Synthesizer is the abstract base class for an object that synthesizes some type of class.
Unihandle
          Class Unihandle is the base class for all M2MI unihandle objects.
